-- European Shares Rise as BP Rallies; Benchmark Stoxx 600 Index Climbs 0.5%
-- David Merritt
-- 2010-06-17T08:42:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/stocks-rise-in-europe-as-bp-rallies-after-obama-meeting-u-s-futures-gain.html

          
          
             European shares gained as a rally in
BP Plc shares offset declines by basic resources companies.  
 The benchmark Stoxx Europe 600 Index advanced 0.5 percent
to 255.61 at 9:41 a.m. in London. BP surged 7.7 percent to 363.1
pence.  
          
          


  


        